column1: NGR is between Abbylands and The Ferns, which an earlier census stated St Marys Lodge was between.
Altitudes match but distance from church is 1 miles versus 0.5 miles quoted.
1911 census suggests that St Marys Lodge is in Pine Grove but does not menton the observer, W Talbot Agar. Pine Grove is 1.3km NNE.
I can find many references to the observer, W Talbot Agar, living at St Marys Lodge, Weybridge but no street name.
